responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "5BA3E37C4DE8698553673CA765A992CA", "The shipments here have been delayed lately, there\'s not much we can really do about this. I can\'t say I\'ve stood here for very long, on most days, usually this is an ordinary courtesy for the porter, but these days we are in the habit of waiting for what may or may not arrive, as many hindrances assail even the sturdiest of hauls in this ramshackle livelihood of ours")
